<bibRefCitation author="Browne, FG" journalOrPublisher="Revue de Zoologie Africaine" pageId="7" pageNumber="164" pagination="773 - 779" title="Some new species of Scolytidae and Platypodidae from Africa and the Seychelles Islands." volume="94" year="1980">Browne 1980: 774.</bibRefCitation>
